        "subject": "LU-169 layout: add incompat flag for lmm_stripe_count change",
        "message": "LU-169 layout: add incompat flag for lmm_stripe_count change\n\nAdd an incompat flag for lustre version which cannot deal with a\n16-bit lmm_stripe_count. This flag will be set in last_rcvd only once\nwe start modifying file layouts, but at least the current version\nshould be confused by a 16-bit stripe count and a non-null generation.\n\nSigned-off-by: Johann Lombardi <johann@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ib02b01df4731a15e8805b849a919f3c020bcaa07\n"
      },
